		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You are fortunate indeed, with a patron that rewards both the stoking and the cooling of your wrath.&nbsp; You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your Strength or Wisdom score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Half your cleric levels count as berserker levels for the purpose of calculating the number of times you can rage between long rests.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When you reduce a creature with a CR equal to half your character level or more to 0 hit points with a melee weapon attack or cleric spell, you regain a use of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.s4iiatrup3e3virw]{Channel Divinity}.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When you exit a rage, choose one of the following:</p>\n</li>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You heal hit points equal to your proficiency bonus + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You regain two points of exertion.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You regain an expended first-level spell slot.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You can end one of the following conditions on yourself: Blinded, Charmed, Confused, Deafened, Frightened, Incapacitated, Paralyzed, Petrified, Rattled, Slowed, or Stunned.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
